title: Moon Hunters (Beta 3)
description:
Moon Hunters is a 1-4 player co-operative action RPG in a rich, ancient world that's different every time you play. Build your mythology as every action and choice contributes to how you're remembered, as a legendary constellation in the night sky for generations to come.

On your search for the missing Moon goddess, you will travel the world with your fellow Hunters and become a living legend for your deeds. How will you be remembered by your tribe in generations to come?
